<msbt attribsize="4">
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00">你<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是住在这座岛上的人吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就住在附近的岛上，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我叫<colour id="3" />巴猎<colour id="65535" />，很高兴认识你！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也可以叫我阿猎哦！<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈哈！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="4" />虽然没有人会这么叫我<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00">这个暂且不说<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之所以来这里呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是因为听说最近很多人<delay8 />
都在暗中关注这座<tag a="110" b="34" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想参考一下，建造出自己理想的<colour id="1" />社区<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以特地过来参观！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00">而且我听说<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这里最初是个无人岛，<delay20 />
现在如此繁华，真让人大吃一惊！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />改造这里的人，<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难道就是你？<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="001_04" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，<delay20 />如果你愿意的话，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也可以来我的岛上玩哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要在<colour id="1" />机场<colour id="65535" />的柜台<delay20 />
说想去<colour id="1" />阿猎的岛<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就可以啦！</message>
	<message label="001_05" attrib="00 00 00 00">那么，我就先在<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />岛上散散步，放松一下喽。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00">我对拍照很有兴趣，<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以就把自己家<delay8 />
弄成了一间还可以的<colour id="1" />摄影棚<colour id="65535" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要是喜欢的话，
可以过来拍照哦。
</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想要找我的话，<delay20 />
就到<colour id="1" />机场<colour id="65535" />的柜台，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说你想去<colour id="1" />阿猎的岛<colour id="65535" />！</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00">我想让我的岛也像这座岛一样发展起来，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让大家看看我建设的理想社区！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈哈！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="4" />虽然还只有我一个人而已<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00">你也是来这座岛观光的？<10_4 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也是的呢，<delay8 />
这座岛真不错啊。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />偶尔和同样来旅游的人聊一聊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也是旅行的乐趣所在呢。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00">我感觉你身上的气息
和这座岛上的居民不一样哦<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座岛上的人有<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd01" />的气味，<delay8 />
而你身上的气味，怎么说呢，
是<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的味道吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />别看我这样，我鼻子很灵哦，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呀，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="1" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然在这里遇到你，<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是有缘啊。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能在旅游的地方与熟人不期而遇，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />世界真是小啊。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="1" />，<delay8 />最近怎么样？<10_4 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是有空的话，<delay20 />
可以再来我的岛上玩哦！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00">你<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
是住在<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座岛上的人？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是从附近的岛过来玩的，<delay20 />
这里真是个很不错的地方呢！</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在旅行地和偶尔同行的人<delay8 />
交谈的那片刻时光<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是所谓旅行的意义吧。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00">你是不是很感兴趣，我是怎么知道<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是这座岛上的人的？<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为我能感觉到<delay8 />你身上有着
和这座岛的居民相同的气味哦<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没错，<delay20 />那就是
刚刚采摘的<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd01" />的气味<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这么看来，<delay8 />
我鼻子相当灵呢，<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈<delay frames="4" />哈<delay frames="4" />哈！</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />也不知道何时才能再见面，<delay20 />
到那时，你和我，<delay20 />
应该还记得对方吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />不管如何，
再见到的话，就和我打招呼吧！</message>
</msbt>